osen for the specific and detailed studies the project reports cover the analysis of electricity sector dynamics at the state level and their influence on the investment technology type and size fuel choice and operational practices at the plant level the assessment sheds light on the impacts of reforms dynamics on the ownership risks investment flows market structure and emissions baseline at the state and sector levels an important contribution of the project is a comparative analysis of indian states with the chinese provinces of guangdong liaoning and hubei search search within everything courses events fellowships news op eds people publications research other pages support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 724 1714 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
